# Keep processed data, models, results, figures (needed for Streamlit Cloud)
# data/processed/ → parquet files needed by dashboard
# data/models/    → trained model pkl/pt files
# data/results/   → evaluation JSON/pkl
# data/figures/   → report plots

# Exclude only the huge RF model until retrained (646MB > GitHub 100MB limit)
# After running: python src/models/train_all.py  → rf_model.pkl will be ~40MB
# Then remove this line:
# data/models/rf_model.pkl

